LEFT JOIN:
List all of the VIPs (last name, first name) and the event they are leading, if any, ordered by the VIPs last name.
SELECT vips.last_name
, vips.first_name
, events.event_name
FROM vips
LEFT JOIN events
ON vips.event = events.event_id
ORDER BY vips.last_name
;

INNER JOIN:
Make a list of all of the events (sorted alphabetically). Include the type of event, the name of the association 
of the VIP presenting, and the name of the VIP presenting (last, first).
SELECT events.event_name
, events.event_type
, vips.association
, vips.last_name
, vips.first_name
FROM vips
INNER JOIN events
ON vips.event = events.event_id
ORDER BY events.event_name
;

Multiple JOINs:
List all the VIPs who are staying at the Marriott and who have RSVP'd "Yes" to the welcome party. Include the hotel name in results.
SELECT vips.last_name
, vips.first_name
, hotels.hotel_name
FROM vips
INNER JOIN reservations
ON vips.member_id = reservations.member_id
INNER JOIN hotels
ON reservations.hotel = hotels.hotel_id
WHERE reservations.welcome_rsvp = 1
AND hotels.hotel_name = 'Marriott'
ORDER BY vips.last_name
;

Query with a subquery:
Recognize the VIPs who have been a member for 10 years or more who are attending the thank you dinner.
SELECT last_name
, first_name
, member_since
FROM vips
WHERE member_since <= 2016
AND member_id IN (SELECT member_id
FROM reservations
WHERE dinner_rsvp = 1)
;

SELF JOIN:
Show the name of which VIP is giving feedback to which presenter in alphabetical order of the presenters.
SELECT presenters.last_name AS presenter_last_name
, presenters.first_name AS presenter_first_name
, evaluators.last_name AS evaluator_last_name
, evaluators.first_name AS evaluator_first_name
FROM vips AS presenters
JOIN vips AS evaluators
ON presenters.member_id = evaluators.provides_feedback_to
ORDER BY presenter_last_name
;

Custom Query:
Provide a list of all VIPs who have RSVP'd yes to the Welcome Party and the Thank You Dinner as well as 
the name of the hotel where they are staying. Provide them in alphabetical order for the hotel for easy pickup.
SELECT COUNT(vips.last_name)
FROM vips 
INNER JOIN reservations
ON vips.member_id = reservations.member_id
INNER JOIN hotels
ON reservations.hotel = hotels.hotel_id
WHERE welcome_rsvp = 1
AND dinner_rsvp = 1
;
